  <summary date="2021-08-09T11:09:21Z" status="Introduced in House">Ensuring Second Amendment Freedoms are Executed Timely Act

This bill allows a licensed gun dealer, manufacturer, or importer to transfer a firearm to an unlicensed person if a submitted background check remains incomplete after three calendar days (currently, three business days).</summary>
